text: Kobiałka may refer to the following places in Poland: *Kobiałka, Legnica County in Gmina Chojnów, Legnica County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (SW Poland) *Kobiałka (Warsaw), a neighborhood in Białołęka in the north-eastern part of Warsaw *Kobiałka (Milicz), part of the town Milicz, in the northern part of Lower Silesian Voivodeship (SW Poland) *Kobiałka (województwo łódzkie), part of the village of Stare Krasnodęby in Gmina Aleksandrów Łódzki in the district of Zgierz in Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) ==See also== * Kobiałki, a village in Gmina Wieczfnia Kościelna, Mława County, Masovian Voivodeship, in east-central Poland
title: Kobiałka
